<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mentor Homepage</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: url('https://png.pngtree.com/thumb_back/fh260/background/20230613/pngtree-black-and-white-gym-room-with-a-row-of-equipment-image_2911173.jpg') center center fixed;
            background-size: cover;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #007bff;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .action-buttons {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

            .action-buttons a {
                display: inline-block;
                padding: 10px 20px;
                margin: 5px;
                background-color: #007bff;
                color: #fff;
                text-decoration: none;
                border-radius: 5px;
                transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            }

                .action-buttons a:hover {
                    background-color: #0056b3;
                }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Mentor Homepage</h1>
        <p>Welkom bij de mentoren homepage</p>
        <p>Hier kan u het rooster zien van de lessons en gebruikers verwijderen van lessons.</p>
        <p>Klik op een van de onderstaande knoppen om naar de verschillende opties te gaan:</p>
        <div class="action-buttons">
            <a asp-action="Userlessons">Gebruiker lessons aanpassen</a>
            <a asp-action="Lessonslist">lessons lijst</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>